title: 144: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (May '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (May '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey are taste-testing a slew of amazing finds like vegan taco salad, a tasty Russian ravioli, vegan Bolognese, roasted cauliflower, roasted green beans, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new jackfruit item that’s REALLY YUMMY! So don’t go anywhere… Push play now, and when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We’re back for another SUPER-FUN and DELICIOUS haul from Trader Joe’s!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
